{"tid":687451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Marvel】「奇異博士」班尼迪1個打4個 勇救外賣仔","createTime":"2018-06-02T09:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T16:07:09.000Z","uid":29314,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3bbafb4c4d6480e951e44128d6d04b6ba6b03830","tid":687451,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:22:05.000Z","msg":"在電影中扮演超級英雄「奇異博士」的英國型男影星班尼迪甘巴貝治(Benedict Cumberbatch)，現實生活中原來也是英雄，曾以一敵四，救回一名被圍毆的「外賣仔」。<br />\n<br />\n53歲的Uber司機戴亞斯(Manuel Dias)說，在去年11月25日晚上約9時半，他載著班尼迪及其妻往倫敦一間會所，但經過馬里利邦尼高街(Marylebone High Street)時，見到4名惡棍正圍毆外賣公司Deliveroo一名單車外賣員。<br />\n<br />\n班尼迪毫不猶疑跳下車，拉開4名惡棍，高喊「不要搞他」。該4名拿著玻璃樽的流氓，企圖出拳打他，但被他擋開和推開。戴亞斯見情勢不對，下車想幫手，此時他才認出班尼迪，而4名流氓此時亦逃去。"},{"pid":"7867518d21c9ab5e78023682cd979ecc60c37b9b","tid":687451,"uid":33077,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:23:16.000Z","msg":"男神"},{"pid":"af4e3a842ea9dc3f23f34501002eaf781febe356","tid":687451,"uid":33789,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:23:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"081da7644b710e4602a0414585ac78e5996c83a4","tid":687451,"uid":20302,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:24:46.000Z","msg":"會唔會驚佢真係變身 先逃走"},{"pid":"b19f4999dbda97977bf54c4cbf5a50de96264ae0","tid":687451,"uid":20899,"like":15,"dislike":4,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:25:38.000Z","msg":"係咪marvel啲彩蛋"},{"pid":"1614ebfcb6551571701617d4899d622f9ac2a45b","tid":687451,"uid":4880,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:25:40.000Z","msg":"dormammu i've come to bargain"},{"pid":"9c18b204493d323f51169d743ba7dc9eaf0717d9","tid":687451,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:27:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪marvel啲彩蛋</blockquote><br />\n可能拍緊dr strange傳"},{"pid":"95b78b81d5ae9966839dbbc7ac